															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser deleted" data-id="3956486"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/common--images/avatars/default/a16.png" alt=""/>(account deleted)</span> <span class="odate time_1530116697 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">27 Jun 2018 16:24</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3852457">
									

<p>I like Replica too; I really like how somber it is. I dig Gardens of Delete too.</p>
<p>Clarence's most recent singles sound way cleaner then the ones from No Now. They still sound good, with that &quot;a-choir-of-bee-producing-pop&quot; quality, but I kinda miss the abrasive earcandy (a term coined by Anthony Fantano, the internet's busiest music nerd) vibe.</p>
<p>What do you think of Death Grips?</p>

							</div>

								
					
