														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3853154">
									

<p>Yeah, Andy Morrin is a seriously underrated producer in my opinion (I know he's lowkey and not active outside of DG but, c'mon). That dude is capable of embedding chaos and euphoria into beats, like in &quot;Inanimate Sensation&quot;.</p>
<p>&quot;Government Plates&quot; is my least favorite project. It's strange how every single Death Grips album can be this person's favorite and another's least. I recommend giving &quot;Fashion Week&quot; a listen if you haven't, since Andy has more creative influence in that project.</p>

							</div>

								
					
